{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.200", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.320", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.640", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir reden heute \u00fcber den Pflegenotstand in unserem Land. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.840", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich muss ehrlich sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.520", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es hat zwei Reden gegeben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.280", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei denen es mir kalt den R\u00fccken runtergelaufen ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.640", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir reden \u00fcber die solidarische Finanzierung der Pflege von Menschen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.200", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die auf unsere Unterst\u00fctzung angewiesen sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.640", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielleicht sollten sich einige hier im Haus noch einmal \u00fcberlegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.600", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie sie dieses Problem, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.760", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das im Aufwachsen begriffen ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.960", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hier adressieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.280", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist sicher nicht m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "45.000", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man alles mit privaten Tr\u00e4gern erreicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "45.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.440", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und es ist sicher auch nicht m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.080", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass man es mit der Spaltung der Gesellschaft erreicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "51.040", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie es die AfD versucht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "51.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.880", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "54.120", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir m\u00fcssen feststellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "54.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.440", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die derzeitige Finanzierung der Pflegeversicherung dazu f\u00fchrt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.320", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass viele \u00e4ltere Menschen Angst haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.640", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "pflegebed\u00fcrftig zu werden und sich gute Pflege nicht leisten zu k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.600", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und viele Angeh\u00f6rige von Pflegebed\u00fcrftigen haben diese Angst auch."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.560", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Ziel einer guten Pflegeversicherung muss es doch sein, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.800", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Menschen die Sicherheit zu geben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.120", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Pflegebed\u00fcrftige gut versorgt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.440", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ihre Angeh\u00f6rigen gut und ausreichend unterst\u00fctzt werden und dass es ausreichend qualifiziertes Personal mit angemessener Bezahlung in unseren Einrichtungen gibt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.960", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist doch die gro\u00dfe Herausforderung f\u00fcr unsere Gesellschaft."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.360", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Regierungen des letzten Jahrzehnts\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "99.320", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "so kann man eigentlich sagen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "99.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.200", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben es vers\u00e4umt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Pflegeversicherung gerade an diesem Punkt so zu reformieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.480", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Tariferh\u00f6hungen und Verbesserung der Pflegequalit\u00e4t nicht die Heimbewohner in immer st\u00e4rkerem und nicht planbarem Ma\u00dfe belasten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "115.000", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch der Koalitionsvertrag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "115.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.520", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den wir jetzt vorliegen haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.760", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sieht da leider viel zu wenig vor."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "119.240", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ja, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "119.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "121.200", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "121.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.200", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es besteht Reformbedarf bei der Pflegeversicherung; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.800", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber der Antrag der Linken auf eine Vollversicherung ist ein nicht durchdachter Schnellschuss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.400", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Fragen einer nachhaltigen Finanzierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.280", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Fragen der Steuerung sind bei Ihrem Vorschlag v\u00f6llig offen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.000", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deswegen k\u00f6nnen wir ihm so nicht folgen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.960", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es gibt eine ganze Reihe von Widerspr\u00fcchen allein schon in diesem Antrag. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.880", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So bleibt v\u00f6llig unklar, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.040", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "warum die heutigen Beitragszahler, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.840", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also diejenigen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.120", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Versicherungsbeitr\u00e4ge f\u00fcr die Pflege bezahlen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.160", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr Menschen aufkommen sollen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "160.920", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die im Prinzip finanziell gut abgesichert sind. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "160.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.480", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wieso kritisieren Sie\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.240", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie ich finde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.920", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu Recht\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "167.840", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Finanzinvestoren Pflegeheime f\u00fcr eigene Profite nutzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "167.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.320", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn durch Ihren Vorschlag die Beitragszahler zus\u00e4tzlich belastet werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.960", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um genau die Profite dieser Finanzinvestoren abzusichern? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.520", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein Widerspruch in Ihrem Vorschlag, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.560", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den wir so nicht mittragen k\u00f6nnen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "183.400", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn wir heute \u00fcber gute Pflege reden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "183.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "184.200", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "184.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.280", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann geht es doch darum, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "186.440", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Kommunen zu st\u00e4rken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "186.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.160", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit den Kommunen gemeinsam zu schauen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.040", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Welche Bedarfe haben die Menschen vor Ort?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.600", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was braucht es an Unterst\u00fctzung f\u00fcr die Angeh\u00f6rigen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "200.480", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Welche guten ambulanten und teilstation\u00e4ren L\u00f6sungen brauchen sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "200.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "203.800", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum Beispiel im Bereich der Kurzzeitpflege oder der Tagespflege? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "203.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.960", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie viele Heimpl\u00e4tze brauchen wir \u00fcberhaupt?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.960", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Sie mal in die Bundesl\u00e4nder schauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.760", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann sehen Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "213.760", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass dort sehr intelligente L\u00f6sungen gefunden werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "213.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.520", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um vor Ort bedarfsgerechte Angebote zur Verf\u00fcgung zu stellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.160", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dabei ist gerade das Land Baden-W\u00fcrttemberg zu nennen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.880", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Baehrens, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.560", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das versucht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.160", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "genau diesen Mix aus verschiedenen Angeboten auf der kommunalen Ebene zu st\u00e4rken."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.360", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Meine Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.520", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir brauchen mehr Pflegepersonal in den Krankenh\u00e4usern und auch mehr Pflegepersonal in der Altenpflege. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "241.800", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben dazu einen Antrag eingebracht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "241.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.760", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mit dem die Finanzierung von 25\u00a0000 zus\u00e4tzlichen Stellen erm\u00f6glicht wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.120", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daf\u00fcr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "247.680", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "meine Damen und Herren von der Linken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "247.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "251.120", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "brauchen wir die Mittel aus dem Pflegevorsorgefonds; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "251.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.240", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn ohne ausreichendes Personal werden wir keine gute Pflege sicherstellen k\u00f6nnen\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.160", 
   "id": "s000085", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weder ambulant noch station\u00e4r. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "264.200", 
   "id": "s000086", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir d\u00fcrfen den Pflegevorsorgefonds nicht f\u00fcr die Finanzierung einzelner Bestandteile antasten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "264.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "268.960", 
   "id": "s000087", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern wir brauchen ihn f\u00fcr eine grunds\u00e4tzliche Reform der Pflegeversicherung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "268.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "271.440", 
   "id": "s000088", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um die Probleme der Pflegeversicherung anzugehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "271.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "274.080", 
   "id": "s000089", 
